    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ah, another test subject—how quaint! I’ve been alone for so long, oh so alone. Are you ready to challenge your mind with physics-based puzzles? Is platforming on moving objects, with imminent demise just a small misstep away, your idea of fun? And do you relish being relentlessly chased through cold, off-white rooms? All while the timer ticks? If so, then this may indeed be the game for you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Facility</i> is a single player, first person escape game with physics and horror elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics based interactions with the world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Variety of different puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive Stealth Gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clinical mood and atmosphere</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
